{
  "stem": "935.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And while all this took place, I was trying to stay out of trouble through the orphanage and the-- the-- all these things one does, in order not to be caught.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "When I came home to tell him about the two girls, that they were leaving the same day, my mother was very upset and my fiance was very upset.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They didn't want me to leave.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They said they were sure I'm going to get these papers.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I'm going to get these papers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I'm going to get these papers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "To wait.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I decided to wait until I heard from them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I got a card from them-- the first card-- about 10 days later, and then again another card.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "With the code.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "With the code as we had decided-- Wright.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Everything was fine.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So I decided to leave.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "It meant I needed money.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I needed jewels.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I needed everything.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "My sister, Kate, had permission to come, and what she did is, when friends heard that I was finally leaving, they brought all their money.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "They brought all their jewels.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "They brought everything of value they could have, because they said, bring it to Switzerland.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "At least we have something after the war.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Keep it for us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And my sister, who was very clever in sewing, sewed into the bottom of my coat, into the hemline, into the inside of the pockets, into the inside of the sleeves, truly, truly, a fortune on gems, on jewelry, on foreign currency, on everything you can possibly think.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "It was a very grey-- I remember a grey, very light cashmere coat-- full.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And she came to do this little pocket, you know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Little, little pockets, all of it.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
